node.text:
In this video you can see my notes I took in the first week of uni. Now in this notebook are only notes for 4 subjects and not everything at all! Just lectures that were a bit hard to memorise. I merged my notes from class + from the powerpoint presentations that our professors sent to us. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
notebook: Mar Mar A5 Grid Business College Block
black pen: Faber Castell Grip x5 in 0.5
colored pens: Staedtler Triplus Fineliners, Pilot Juice in 0.38
highlighters: Mildliners
.
.
.
.

[ t u e - 20/07 ] 🐁🍊🛋

feeling content. 
i got my results yesterday, and seeing “ADMIS” (admitted) next to my assigned number lifted a weight i’ve been struggling to hold. because  even tho i’ve been postive about my application, the day before results day: fear got the best of me.
we celebrated with a baclava and my mom made apple pie. it was a good day 🍰🍽

i know some of you friends applied to uni as well this year. i hope it went well & congratulations!! ❣️

if you didn’t recieve the results you hoped for, i hope you’ll find the peace & support you need now. sending a big warm hug ʕっ• ᴥ • ʔっ
